'''Thornwood''' is a master [[planned community]] of single-family homes and townhomes located in [[South Elgin]], [[Illinois]] at the intersection of Silver Glen and Randall Roads on over {{convert|750|acre|km2}} of land and centered on a $3.8 million clubhouse that is situated on {{convert|6|acre|m2}} of land. Construction started in 1998 and finished in 2005, three years ahead of schedule.<ref name="Crown">[http://www.cciland.com/cmmnty.htm Thornwood Homes - The Community<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref>

